      <hedline>
        <hl1>Who's Glacial Now?</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Jeanne Fudala letter holds that problem is that term 'glacial pace' now applies only to Bush administration, not to glaciers (April 28 editorial)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''A Glacial Pace on Warming'' (editorial, April 28):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''A Glacial Pace on Warming'' (editorial, April 28):</p>
        <p>The problem in a nutshell is that the term ''glacial pace'' now applies only to the administration in Washington, not to the glaciers!</p>
        <p>Jeanne Fudala  Alpine, N.Y., May 1, 2007</p>
      </block>
